<br>
One strat I have seen used is to have the main tank with his back into the corner with everyone else behind the mob beating him into the corner. This keeps him in one location and facing the right direction assuming your other tanks can control aggro. Can be a little troublesom when you switch main tanks.<br>
<br>
As for the dmg output giant bane wizzys are great, rogues with RB are great, even monks with just epics are great. Also you want to throw every attack buff on people you can. CoP once you get that 60 ranger, Strenght of Nature, bard songs/epic proc. Also if you can manage a 60 shaman or 2 an avatar on a couple main dmg dealers(rogues) can really help thier dmg output. <br>
<br>
It sounds like really the biggest thing you can do is get some lvls. For the most part if you can drop vindi the statue should be easy. He is slowable so he has a lower dmg output just has a higher hps. For most people it's easier to deal with lower dmg output and a longer fight. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.emailToFriend?topicID=9050.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.threadControl?topicID=9050.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=9050.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=9050.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesafehousetherootcellar">The Root Cellar<optio